{"tid":1561812,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"反修例運動激發藍黃絲茅盾","createTime":"2019-09-11T17:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T19:31:43.000Z","uid":152527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d97c661dc5a84b9bd2b5c59c91aa2b0779017d","tid":1561812,"uid":152527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:42:46.000Z","msg":"反修例運動，激發藍黃絲茅盾，上一代藍絲其實佢地唔駛點好既學歷，好易搵到穩定收入。仲有些藍絲其實電腦又唔識英文又唔識拎幾皮野人工<br />\n<br />\n但黃絲努力讀書，捱生捱死，仲要比d垃圾藍絲點反轉頭，仲要幫藍絲廢老執屎！<br />\n<br />\n今次反修例活動，正正比平日比藍絲廢老蝦既黃絲企出黎，爭取應有既野，唔好再比垃圾廢老騎住<br />\n<br />\n同樣既post係香討深藍地方出過，比班廢老用惡毒言論鬧過！"},{"pid":"c2511c787e2c0cf6c73573a0b044d098a1561d90","tid":1561812,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:43:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"049cc592b62e166ec37a6c293764b8085ed7318f","tid":1561812,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:43:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"113bc6ba44f613cc4efc026cf2125d1c5a9cf9b0","tid":1561812,"uid":228092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:45:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>915去完英領去民陣遊行！升級玩國際戰線！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋升級玩國際戰線！繼續遍地開花！每個星期去唔同領事館，舉唔同國旗！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com